<div class="modal wide" id="storageModal"><div class="modal-box"><div class="modal-head"><h2>使用空间一览表 PRO</h2><button onclick="closeStorageCenter()">关闭</button></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="storage-dashboard"><div class="storage-stat"><b id="storTotal">0 B</b><span>已知占用合计</span></div><div class="storage-stat"><b id="storUpload">0 B</b><span>上传资料目录</span></div><div class="storage-stat"><b id="storLogs">0 B</b><span>日志明细 JSON</span></div><div class="storage-stat"><b id="storSnaps">0 B</b><span>快照 JSON</span></div></div><div class="storage-tip">压缩包本身不能像普通图片一样直接预览；本版上传 ZIP 时会自动解压里面的 JPG/PNG/WebP/GIF 到公共图库，所以解压出来的图片可以预览、搜索、确认配对。原 ZIP 也会保留作备份资料。</div><div id="storageWarnings"></div><div class="storage-mini"><div><h3>图片/资料分类占用</h3><div id="storageGroups" class="storage-bars"></div></div><div><h3>数据表占用</h3><div id="storageTables" class="storage-bars"></div></div></div><h3>最近上传文件</h3><div id="storageRecent"></div></div></div></div>
<div class="modal wide" id="settingsModal"><div class="modal-box"><div class="modal-head"><h2>资料系统设置中心 PRO</h2><button onclick="closeSettings()">关闭</button></div><div class="admin-shell"><div class="admin-left"><h3>设置分类</h3><div class="admin-menu"><button class="active" data-set-tab="ui" onclick="setSettingsTab('ui')">界面 / 密度</button><button data-set-tab="layout" onclick="setSettingsTab('layout')">区域大小</button><button data-set-tab="header" onclick="setSettingsTab('header')">我的抬头</button><button data-set-tab="pdf" onclick="setSettingsTab('pdf')">PDF 抬头 / 水印</button><button data-set-tab="category" onclick="setSettingsTab('category')">大类拖动排序</button><button data-set-tab="storage" onclick="setSettingsTab('storage')">空间 / 清理</button><button data-set-tab="security" onclick="setSettingsTab('security')">权限 / 日志规则</button></div><div class="setting-preview" style="margin-top:12px"><h2 id="settingsPreviewTitle">资料生成系统</h2><p id="settingsPreviewSub">Datasheet Center</p><div class="custom-header-preview" style="margin-top:10px"><div class="company" id="settingsPreviewCompany">Artdon Lighting Limited</div><div class="sub">PDF / Datasheet Header Preview</div></div></div></div><div class="admin-main"><div id="setTab-ui" class="set-tab"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card"><h3>字体与密度</h3><div class="desc">调整整个资料系统的视觉密度，避免按钮和文字太粗太大。</div><div class="pro-row"><label>字体大小</label><input id="setFontScale" type="range" min="0.72" max="1.08" step="0.02" oninput="previewSettings()"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>主题</label><select id="setTheme" onchange="previewSettings()"><option value="blue">蓝白</option><option value="green">绿色</option><option value="dark">暗黑</option></select></div><div class="pro-row"><label>列表密度</label><select id="setListDensity"><option value="compact">紧凑</option><option value="normal">标准</option><option value="large">宽松</option></select></div></div><div class="pro-card wide"><h3>首页显示</h3><div class="desc">控制首页大类和产品列表显示，不影响数据库资料。</div><div class="pro-row"><label>首页样式</label><select id="setHomeView"><option value="pro">PRO卡片</option><option value="compact">紧凑卡片</option></select></div><div class="pro-row"><label>顶部在线状态</label><select id="setShowOnlineTop"><option value="1">显示</option><option value="0">隐藏</option></select></div></div></div></div><div id="setTab-layout" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card full"><h3>区域大小</h3><div class="desc">左边产品列表、中间资料编辑、右边 PDF 预览都可以调。适合大屏和笔记本分别保存。</div><div class="pro-row"><label>分类卡宽</label><input id="setCatWidth" type="number" min="150" max="320" step="10"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>产品列表宽</label><input id="setListWidth" type="number" min="280" max="520" step="10"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>详情区宽</label><input id="setDetailWidth" type="number" min="420" max="900" step="10"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF区宽</label><input id="setPdfWidth" type="number" min="520" max="1100" step="10"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF预览高度</label><input id="setPdfHeight" type="number" min="520" max="1280" step="20"></div></div></div></div><div id="setTab-header" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card wide"><h3>我的资料系统抬头</h3><div class="desc">这里填你自己的系统抬头，公司抬头也会用于 PDF/快照。</div><div class="pro-row"><label>系统标题</label><input id="setTitle" oninput="previewSettings()"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>系统副标题</label><input id="setSubtitle" oninput="previewSettings()"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>公司抬头</label><input id="setCompany" placeholder="Artdon Lighting Limited" oninput="previewSettings()"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>自定义抬头区</label><textarea id="setCustomHeaderHtml" rows="5" placeholder="可写展会版本、客户版本、内部版本说明"></textarea></div></div></div></div><div id="setTab-pdf" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card"><h3>PDF 抬头</h3><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF抬头开关</label><select id="setPdfHeaderEnabled"><option value="0">不显示</option><option value="1">显示</option></select></div><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF抬头标题</label><input id="setPdfHeaderTitle" placeholder="Artdon Lighting Limited"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF抬头副标题</label><input id="setPdfHeaderSubtitle" placeholder="Architectural Lighting Datasheet"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>PDF页脚文字</label><input id="setPdfFooterText" placeholder="Artdon Lighting Limited"></div></div><div class="pro-card"><h3>水印</h3><div class="pro-row"><label>显示水印</label><select id="setWatermarkEnabled"><option value="0">不显示</option><option value="1">显示</option></select></div><div class="pro-row"><label>水印文字</label><input id="setWatermarkText"></div><div class="pro-row"><label>水印透明</label><input id="setWatermarkOpacity" type="number" min="0.02" max="0.25" step="0.01"></div></div></div></div><div id="setTab-category" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card full"><h3>大类顺序 · 拖动排序</h3><div class="desc">按住左侧 ≡ 拖动排序。保存后首页大类按此顺序显示，未排序大类自动排后面。</div><div class="cat-order-tools"><button onclick="buildCategoryOrderFromCurrent()">读取当前大类</button><button onclick="clearCategoryOrder()">清空排序</button></div><div id="categoryOrderList" class="cat-order-list drag-pro-list"></div><textarea id="setCategoryOrder" style="display:none"></textarea></div></div></div><div id="setTab-storage" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card full"><h3>使用空间 / 资料清理</h3><div class="desc">查看日志、快照、高清图、配件图、配光曲线、测试资料等占用。清理功能后续按权限单独做，当前先提供准确统计与最近上传。</div><div class="item-actions"><button class="primary" onclick="openStorageCenter()">打开空间一览表</button><button onclick="loadStorageOverview()">刷新空间统计</button></div><div id="settingsStorageInline" style="margin-top:12px"></div></div></div></div><div id="setTab-security" class="set-tab" style="display:none"><div class="pro-grid"><div class="pro-card wide"><h3>权限 / 日志规则</h3><div class="desc">权限仍接统一权限；这里放资料系统管理入口。</div><div class="item-actions"><button class="warn" onclick="openPerms()">打开资料权限</button><button onclick="openLogCenter()">打开日志中心</button><button onclick="openOnlineCenter()">打开在线中心</button></div></div></div></div><div class="item-actions" style="margin-top:14px"><button class="primary" onclick="saveSettings()">保存设置</button><button onclick="resetLocalSettings()">恢复默认</button></div></div></div></div></div>
<div class="modal wide" id="snapshotModal"><div class="modal-box"><div class="modal-head"><h2>资料快照中心 PRO</h2><button onclick="closeSnapshotCenter()">关闭</button></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="snapshot-filter-grid"><input id="snapKw" placeholder="关键词：型号 / 客户 / 邮箱 / 备注" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')loadAllSnapshots()"><input id="snapCustomer" placeholder="客户"><input id="snapModel" placeholder="型号"><button class="primary" onclick="loadAllSnapshots()">搜索快照</button></div><div class="snapshot-grid"><div id="snapshotList" class="snapshot-list"><div class="empty">点击搜索查看所有保存过的快照。</div></div><div id="snapshotView" class="snapshot-view"><div class="empty">选择左侧快照查看当时保存的参数、资料、配件、配光曲线、发送给谁。</div></div></div></div></div></div>
<div class="modal wide" id="logModal"><div class="modal-box"><div class="modal-head"><h2>资料系统日志中心 PRO</h2><button onclick="closeLogCenter()">关闭</button></div><div class="panel-body"><div class="log-filter-grid"><input id="logKw" placeholder="关键词：操作 / 型号 / 人员 / 内容" onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')loadLogs()"><input id="logUser" placeholder="操作人"><input id="logModel" placeholder="型号"><select id="logAction"><option value="">全部动作</option><option value="product">产品使用</option><option value="override">参数修改</option><option value="website">官网下载</option><option value="file">上传/配对/删除资料</option><option value="settings">设置</option><option value="snapshot">快照</option><option value="send">发送记录</option><option value="generate">生成资料</option><option value="permission">权限</option><option value="api.error">错误</option></select><input id="logSection" placeholder="版块：PDF/配件/配光/快照"><select id="logSource"><option value="">全部来源</option><option value="official_website_pdf">官网PDF</option><option value="manual_public_library">公共图库上传</option><option value="manual_product_upload">产品资料上传</option><option value="public_library">公共库配对</option><option value="local_generated">系统生成</option></select><input id="logFileType" placeholder="资料类型：PDF/配光/配件/高清"><input id="logDateFrom" type="date"><input id="logDateTo" type="date"><button class="primary" onclick="loadLogs()">筛选日志</button></div><div id="logCenterList" class="log-list" style="max-height:660px"></div></div></div></div>
<script>
const API='datasheet_api.php';
let state={cats:[],products:[],current:null,perms:{},selected:new Set(),activeCat:'',page:1,total:0,accType:'配件',permData:null,permSelected:null,configType:'芯片',configSelected:{芯片:[],光学:[],电源:[],配件:[]}};

let dsSettings={};
function applySettings(set){dsSettings=set||dsSettings||{};let ui=dsSettings.ui||{},head=dsSettings.header||{},wm=dsSettings.watermark||{};document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-font-scale',ui.font_scale||'.88');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-cat-w',(ui.cat_card_width||190)+'px');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-list-w',(ui.product_list_width||360)+'px');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-detail-w','minmax('+(ui.detail_width||520)+'px,1fr)');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-pdf-w',(ui.pdf_width||720)+'px');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-pdf-h',(ui.pdf_height||820)+'px');document.body.classList.toggle('ds-theme-dark',ui.theme==='dark');document.body.classList.toggle('ds-theme-green',ui.theme==='green');document.body.classList.toggle('watermark-layer',String(wm.enabled)==='1');document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-watermark',JSON.stringify(wm.text||''));document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--ds-watermark-opacity',wm.opacity||'.08');if(head.title&&document.querySelector('.brand h1'))document.querySelector('.brand h1').textContent=head.title;if(head.subtitle&&document.querySelector('.brand p'))document.querySelector('.brand p').textContent=head.subtitle;}
function sortCatsBySettings(){let order=(dsSettings.category_order||[]).map(x=>String(x).trim()).filter(Boolean);if(!order.length)return;let pos={};order.forEach((x,i)=>pos[x]=i);state.cats.sort((a,b)=>((pos[a.category]??9999)-(pos[b.category]??9999))||String(a.category).localeCompare(String(b.category),'zh-CN'));}
function currentCategoryNames(){let names=(state.cats||[]).map(c=>c.category).filter(Boolean);let order=(dsSettings.category_order||[]).map(x=>String(x).trim()).filter(Boolean);let seen={};let out=[];order.concat(names).forEach(x=>{if(x&&!seen[x]){seen[x]=1;out.push(x)}});return out;}
function renderCategoryOrderEditor(list){let box=$('categoryOrderList'); if(!box) return; let counts={};(state.cats||[]).forEach(c=>counts[c.category]=c.count||0); let arr=list||currentCategoryNames(); box.innerHTML=''; arr.forEach(name=>{let div=document.createElement('div');div.className='cat-order-item';div.draggable=true;div.dataset.name=name;div.innerHTML='<span class="handle">≡</span><span>'+esc(name)+'</span><span class="count">'+(counts[name]||0)+' 个</span>';div.addEventListener('dragstart',e=>{div.classList.add('dragging');e.dataTransfer.setData('text/plain',name)});div.addEventListener('dragend',()=>{div.classList.remove('dragging');syncCategoryOrderTextarea()});div.addEventListener('dragover',e=>{e.preventDefault();let dragging=box.querySelector('.dragging');if(!dragging||dragging===div)return;let rect=div.getBoundingClientRect();let after=e.clientY>rect.top+rect.height/2;if(after)box.insertBefore(dragging,div.nextSibling);else box.insertBefore(dragging,div)});box.appendChild(div)});syncCategoryOrderTextarea();}
function syncCategoryOrderTextarea(){let arr=[...document.querySelectorAll('#categoryOrderList .cat-order-item')].map(x=>x.dataset.name).filter(Boolean); if($('setCategoryOrder')) $('setCategoryOrder').value=arr.join('\n');}
function buildCategoryOrderFromCurrent(){renderCategoryOrderEditor((state.cats||[]).map(c=>c.category).filter(Boolean));}
function clearCategoryOrder(){renderCategoryOrderEditor([]);$('setCategoryOrder').value='';}
function fillSettingsForm(){let s=dsSettings||{},ui=s.ui||{},h=s.header||{},w=s.watermark||{};$('setFontScale').value=ui.font_scale||'.88';$('setTheme').value=ui.theme||'blue';$('setPdfHeight').value=ui.pdf_height||820;$('setCatWidth').value=ui.cat_card_width||190;$('setListWidth').value=ui.product_list_width||360;$('setDetailWidth').value=ui.detail_width||520;$('setPdfWidth').value=ui.pdf_width||720;$('setTitle').value=h.title||'资料生成系统';$('setSubtitle').value=h.subtitle||'';$('setCompany').value=h.company||'Artdon Lighting Limited';$('setPdfHeaderEnabled').value=String(h.pdf_header_enabled||0);$('setPdfHeaderTitle').value=h.pdf_header_title||h.company||'Artdon Lighting Limited';$('setPdfHeaderSubtitle').value=h.pdf_header_subtitle||'Architectural Lighting Datasheet';$('setPdfFooterText').value=h.pdf_footer_text||h.company||'Artdon Lighting Limited';$('setWatermarkText').value=w.text||'';$('setWatermarkEnabled').value=String(w.enabled||0);$('setWatermarkOpacity').value=w.opacity||.08;$('setCategoryOrder').value=(s.category_order||[]).join('\n');renderCategoryOrderEditor(s.category_order&&s.category_order.length?s.category_order:currentCategoryNames())}
function readSettingsForm(){syncCategoryOrderTextarea();return {ui:{font_scale:$('setFontScale').value,theme:$('setTheme').value,pdf_height:$('setPdfHeight').value,cat_card_width:$('setCatWidth').value,product_list_width:$('setListWidth').value,detail_width:$('setDetailWidth').value,pdf_width:$('setPdfWidth').value},header:{title:$('setTitle').value,subtitle:$('setSubtitle').value,company:$('setCompany').value,pdf_header_enabled:$('setPdfHeaderEnabled').value,pdf_header_title:$('setPdfHeaderTitle').value,pdf_header_subtitle:$('setPdfHeaderSubtitle').value,pdf_footer_text:$('setPdfFooterText').value},watermark:{text:$('setWatermarkText').value,enabled:Number($('setWatermarkEnabled').value),opacity:$('setWatermarkOpacity').value},category_order:$('setCategoryOrder').value}}
function openSettings(){fillSettingsForm();$('settingsModal').classList.add('show')}
function closeSettings(){$('settingsModal').classList.remove('show')}
async function saveSettings(){try{let d=await api('settings_save',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify(readSettingsForm())});dsSettings=d.settings||d;applySettings(dsSettings);sortCatsBySettings();renderCats();msg('设置已保存')}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function resetLocalSettings(){if(!confirm('恢复资料系统默认界面设置？'))return;dsSettings={ui:{font_scale:.88,theme:'blue',cat_card_width:190,product_list_width:360,detail_width:520,pdf_width:720,pdf_height:820},category_order:[],header:{title:'资料生成系统',subtitle:'Datasheet Center',company:'Artdon Lighting Limited',pdf_header_enabled:'0',pdf_header_title:'Artdon Lighting Limited',pdf_header_subtitle:'Architectural Lighting Datasheet',pdf_footer_text:'Artdon Lighting Limited'},watermark:{enabled:0,text:'Artdon Lighting',opacity:.08}};fillSettingsForm();applySettings(dsSettings)}
function openSnapshotCenter(){$('snapshotModal').classList.add('show');loadAllSnapshots()}
function closeSnapshotCenter(){$('snapshotModal').classList.remove('show')}
async function loadAllSnapshots(){try{let q=new URLSearchParams();if($('snapKw').value.trim())q.set('kw',$('snapKw').value.trim());let d=await api('snapshots_all',{qs:q.toString()});let b=$('snapshotList');b.innerHTML='';let rows=d.rows||[];if(!rows.length){b.innerHTML='<div class="empty">没有快照。</div>';return}rows.forEach(r=>{let div=document.createElement('div');div.className='item';div.onclick=()=>loadSnapshotDetail(r.id);div.innerHTML='<b>#'+esc(r.id)+' · '+esc(r.model_no)+' · '+esc(r.customer_name||'未填写客户')+'</b><small>'+esc(r.created_by)+' '+esc(r.created_at)+'<br>'+esc(r.customer_email||'')+' '+esc(r.send_note||'')+'</small>';b.appendChild(div)})}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
async function loadSnapshotDetail(id){try{let r=await api('snapshot_detail',{qs:'id='+encodeURIComponent(id)});let snap=r.snapshot||{};let params=snap.params||{};let files=snap.files||[];let curves=snap.photometric_images||[];let acc=snap.manual_accessories||snap.accessories||[];let html='<h3>快照 #'+esc(r.id)+' · '+esc(r.model_no)+'</h3><div class="item"><b>客户</b><small>'+esc(r.customer_name||'')+' '+esc(r.customer_email||'')+'<br>'+esc(r.send_note||'')+'<br>保存：'+esc(r.created_by)+' '+esc(r.created_at)+'</small></div><h3>参数</h3><div class="record-list">';Object.entries(params).forEach(([k,v])=>{html+='<div class="item"><b>'+esc(k)+'</b><small>'+esc(v)+'</small></div>'});html+='</div><h3>配光曲线 '+curves.length+'</h3><div class="record-list">';curves.forEach(x=>html+='<div class="item"><b>'+esc(x.file_title||x.label||x.original_name||'配光曲线')+'</b><small>'+esc(x.url||x.image||'')+'</small></div>');html+='</div><h3>配件 '+acc.length+'</h3><div class="record-list">';acc.forEach(x=>html+='<div class="item"><b>'+esc(x.name_en||x.name_cn||x.file_title||'配件')+'</b><small>'+esc(x.model_no||x.original_name||'')+'</small></div>');html+='</div><details><summary>完整快照JSON</summary><pre class="json-pre">'+esc(JSON.stringify(snap,null,2))+'</pre></details>';$('snapshotView').innerHTML=html}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function openLogCenter(){$('logModal').classList.add('show');loadLogs()}
function closeLogCenter(){$('logModal').classList.remove('show')}
async function loadLogs(){try{let q=new URLSearchParams();if($('logKw').value.trim())q.set('kw',$('logKw').value.trim());let d=await api('logs',{qs:q.toString()});let rows=d.rows||d||[];let b=$('logCenterList');b.innerHTML='';if(!rows.length){b.innerHTML='<div class="empty">没有日志。</div>';return}rows.forEach(r=>{let div=document.createElement('div');div.className='item';div.innerHTML='<b>'+esc(r.action_label||r.action)+' · '+esc(r.result||'')+'</b><small>'+esc(r.display_name||r.username)+' ｜ '+esc(r.model_no||'')+' ｜ '+esc(r.created_at)+'<br>'+esc(r.target_title||'')+'</small>';b.appendChild(div)})}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}

const DS_PLACE_KEY='artdon_datasheet_v207_place';
let searchTimer=null;
const $=id=>document.getElementById(id); const esc=s=>String(s??'').replace(/[&<>'"]/g,c=>({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;',"'":'&#39;','"':'&quot;'}[c]));
function debouncedSearch(){clearTimeout(searchTimer);searchTimer=setTimeout(()=>loadProducts(1),260)}
function savePlace(){try{localStorage.setItem(DS_PLACE_KEY,JSON.stringify({id:state.current?state.current.id:0,model_no:state.current?state.current.model_no:'',kw:$('kw')?$('kw').value:'',item:$('itemFilter')?$('itemFilter').value:'',source:$('sourceFilter')?$('sourceFilter').value:'',cat:state.activeCat,page:state.page,per:$('perPage')?$('perPage').value:'20'}));}catch(e){}}
function loadPlace(){try{return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(DS_PLACE_KEY)||'{}')||{};}catch(e){return {}}}
window.addEventListener('beforeunload',savePlace);
function msg(t,bad=false){const m=$('msg');m.textContent=t;m.className='msg show '+(bad?'err':'ok');clearTimeout(m._t);m._t=setTimeout(()=>m.className='msg',3200)}
async function parseJson(r){const tx=await r.text();try{return JSON.parse(tx)}catch(e){throw new Error('接口不是JSON：'+tx.slice(0,180))}}
async function api(action,opt={}){let url=API+'?action='+encodeURIComponent(action)+(opt.qs?'&'+opt.qs:'');let r=await fetch(url,opt);let j=await parseJson(r);if(!j.ok)throw new Error(j.msg||'操作失败');return j.data}
async function boot(){try{let b=await api('bootstrap');state.perms=b.perms||{};dsSettings=b.settings||{};applySettings(dsSettings);$('stProducts').textContent=b.stats.products||0;$('stFiles').textContent=b.stats.files||0;$('stRecords').textContent=b.stats.records||0;$('stAcc').textContent=b.stats.accessories||0;let old=loadPlace();if(old.kw)$('kw').value=old.kw;if(old.item)$('itemFilter').value=old.item;if(old.source)$('sourceFilter').value=old.source;if(old.per)$('perPage').value=old.per;state.activeCat=old.cat||'';let h=await api('home');state.cats=h.categories||[];sortCatsBySettings();renderCats();await loadProducts(old.page||1);if(old.id){setTimeout(()=>selectProduct(old.id),120)}}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function renderCats(){let b=$('catGrid');b.innerHTML='';if(!state.cats.length){b.innerHTML='<div class="empty">没有读取到命名系统产品分类。</div>';return}state.cats.forEach(c=>{let div=document.createElement('div');div.className='cat-card '+(state.activeCat===c.category?'active':'');div.onclick=()=>{state.activeCat=c.category;renderCats();loadProducts(1);savePlace()};let samples=(c.samples||[]).slice(0,5).map(p=>'<span class="sample-thumb">'+(p.image_url?'<img src="'+esc(p.image_url)+'">':'')+'</span>').join('');div.innerHTML='<div><div class="cat-name">'+esc(c.category)+'</div><div class="cat-count">'+(c.count||0)+' 个产品</div></div><div class="sample-strip">'+samples+'</div>';b.appendChild(div)})}
async function loadProducts(page=1){try{state.page=page;let q=new URLSearchParams();q.set('page',page);q.set('per_page',$('perPage').value||20);if($('kw').value.trim())q.set('kw',$('kw').value.trim());if(state.activeCat)q.set('category',state.activeCat);if($('sourceFilter').value)q.set('source',$('sourceFilter').value);if($('itemFilter').value.trim())q.set('item_name',$('itemFilter').value.trim());let d=await api('products',{qs:q.toString()});state.products=d.rows||[];state.total=d.total||0;renderProducts();savePlace();}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function renderProducts(){let b=$('productList');$('listCount').textContent=state.total||0;b.innerHTML='';if(!state.products.length){b.innerHTML='<div class="empty">没有产品。</div>';return}state.products.forEach(p=>{let div=document.createElement('div');div.className='p-card '+(state.current&&state.current.id===p.id?'active':'');div.onclick=(ev)=>{if(ev.target.tagName==='INPUT')return;selectProduct(p.id)};div.innerHTML='<input type="checkbox" '+(state.selected.has(p.id)?'checked':'')+' onchange="toggleSel('+p.id+',this.checked)"><div class="thumb">'+(p.image_url?'<span class="source-badge '+(p.source_class==='web'?'web':'')+'">'+esc(p.source_label)+'</span><img src="'+esc(p.image_url)+'">':'IMG')+'</div><div><div class="p-title">'+esc(p.model_no)+'</div><div class="p-meta">'+esc(p.category)+' ｜ '+esc(p.type_name)+'<br>'+esc(p.series)+'</div><div class="chips"><span class="chip blue">'+(p.file_count||0)+' 资料</span><span class="chip orange">'+(p.record_count||0)+' 生成</span></div></div>';b.appendChild(div)})}
function toggleSel(id,on){if(on)state.selected.add(id);else state.selected.delete(id)}function selectedIds(){return [...state.selected].filter(Boolean)}function selectAllVisible(){state.products.forEach(p=>state.selected.add(p.id));renderProducts()}function needSelected(){let ids=selectedIds();if(!ids.length&&state.current)ids=[state.current.id];if(!ids.length){msg('请先勾选产品',true);return null}return ids}
function productFromList(id){return (state.products||[]).find(p=>Number(p.id)===Number(id))||null}
const websiteSyncing={};
function websiteSlugFromProduct(p){
  if(!p)return '';
  let u=String(p.source_url||'');
  try{let url=new URL(u,location.href);let slug=url.searchParams.get('slug')||'';if(slug)return slug;let parts=url.pathname.split('/').filter(Boolean);let last=parts.pop()||'';if(last&&!/\.php$/i.test(last))return decodeURIComponent(last);}catch(e){}
  return String(p.web_slug||p.slug||'');
}
function officialPdfUrl(p){let slug=websiteSlugFromProduct(p);if(slug)return 'https://artdonlighting.com/product_pdf.php?slug='+encodeURIComponent(slug)+'&logo=0'; if(p&&p.source_id&&/^\d+$/.test(String(p.source_id)))return 'https://artdonlighting.com/product_pdf.php?id='+encodeURIComponent(p.source_id)+'&logo=0'; return ''}
function shouldFetchWebsite(p){return false; /* V2.0.7：不再点选自动抓官网，必须手动点“拉取当前官网资料” */}
function autoFetchWebsiteCurrent(){
  let p=state.current;if(!shouldFetchWebsite(p))return;
  websiteSyncing[p.id]=1;
  setTimeout(async()=>{
    let startId=p.id;
    try{msg('后台只拉当前产品官网资料，不影响你继续操作...');let d=await api('sync_website_cache',{qs:'id='+encodeURIComponent(startId)+'&model_no='+encodeURIComponent(p.model_no||'')});
      if(state.current&&Number(state.current.id)===Number(startId)){state.current=Object.assign(state.current||{},d);renderDetail(state.current);refreshPdf();msg('当前产品官网参数、配光曲线、配件已缓存');}
    }catch(e){console.warn(e); if(state.current&&Number(state.current.id)===Number(startId))msg('当前产品官网资料拉取失败，可稍后手动重试：'+e.message,true);}
    finally{delete websiteSyncing[startId];}
  },60);
}
async function selectProduct(id){
  const quick=productFromList(id);
  if(quick){state.current=Object.assign({params:{'Product family':quick.series||'','Model':quick.model_no||'','Dimensions':quick.dimension_text||''},files:[],records:[],accessories:[],configs:[]},quick);renderProducts();renderDetail(state.current);refreshPdf();}
  try{let d=await api('product',{qs:'id='+id});state.current=Object.assign(state.current||{},d);renderProducts();renderDetail(state.current);refreshPdf();savePlace();loadRelated(id,false);}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}
}
async function loadRelated(id,rerender=true){if(!state.current)return;try{let d=await api('product_related',{qs:'id='+encodeURIComponent(id||state.current.id)+'&model_no='+encodeURIComponent(state.current.model_no||'')});state.current=Object.assign(state.current,d);if(rerender)renderDetail(state.current);}catch(e){console.warn(e)}}
async function syncWebsiteCache(){if(!state.current)return;try{msg('只拉当前这个产品的官网资料...');let d=await api('sync_website_cache',{qs:'id='+encodeURIComponent(state.current.id)+'&model_no='+encodeURIComponent(state.current.model_no||'')});state.current=Object.assign(state.current||{},d);renderDetail(state.current);refreshPdf();msg('当前产品官网参数、配光曲线、配件已缓存')}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function renderDetail(p){$('detailTitle').textContent=p.model_no;$('detailSub').textContent=p.category+' ｜ '+p.type_name+' ｜ '+p.series;$('detailSource').textContent=p.source_label;$('detailSource').className='chip '+(p.source_class==='web'?'green':'blue');let ov=p.override||{};let pp=p.params||{};let order=['Product family','Model','Dimensions','Cut-out','Power','Luminous flux','Efficacy','Voltage','CCT','CRI','Beam angle','IP rating','Finish','Mounting','Dimming','Material'];let cn={'Product family':'系列','Model':'型号','Dimensions':'尺寸','Cut-out':'开孔','Power':'功率','Luminous flux':'流明','Efficacy':'效率','Voltage':'电压','CCT':'色温','CRI':'显指','Beam angle':'角度','IP rating':'IP','Finish':'表面','Mounting':'安装','Dimming':'调光','Material':'材质'};let params=[];order.forEach(k=>{if(pp[k])params.push([cn[k]||k,pp[k]])});Object.keys(pp).forEach(k=>{if(!order.includes(k)&&pp[k])params.push([k,pp[k]])});let syncNote=(p.is_website?'<div class="source-note">官网同步产品：点选不再自动抓官网，避免卡顿。缺少详细参数/配光曲线/配件时，只点一次这里的“拉取当前官网资料”，系统只拉当前这个型号并写入缓存。</div><div style="margin:6px 0"><button class="mini" onclick="syncWebsiteCache()">拉取当前官网资料</button></div>':'<div class="source-note">命名同步产品：空白字段可在下面补充。</div>');$('tab-base').innerHTML='<div class="media-grid"><div class="media-box"><div class="media-title">产品图（点击预览）</div><div class="media-img" '+(p.image_url?'onclick="openImagePreview(\''+esc(p.image_url)+'\',\'产品图\')"':'')+'>'+(p.image_url?'<img src="'+esc(p.image_url)+'">':'<div class="empty">无产品图</div>')+'</div></div><div class="media-box"><div class="media-title">尺寸图（点击预览）</div><div class="media-img" '+(p.drawing_url?'onclick="openImagePreview(\''+esc(p.drawing_url)+'\',\'尺寸图\')"':'')+'>'+(p.drawing_url?'<img src="'+esc(p.drawing_url)+'">':'<div class="empty">无尺寸图</div>')+'</div></div></div>'+syncNote+'<div class="params">'+params.map(x=>'<div class="param"><label>'+esc(x[0])+'</label><b>'+esc(x[1]||'-')+'</b></div>').join('')+'</div><h3>补充 PDF 参数</h3>'+overrideForm(ov);renderFiles(p.files||[]);renderAccessories(p);renderCurves(p);renderConfig(p);renderRecords(p.records||[])}
function overrideForm(ov){let f=[['title','PDF标题'],['intro','产品介绍'],['product_family','Product family/系列'],['model_display','Model/型号显示'],['dimensions','Dimensions/尺寸'],['cutout','Cut-out/开孔'],['power','功率'],['luminous_flux','流明'],['efficacy','效率'],['voltage','电压'],['cct','色温'],['cri','显指'],['beam_angle','角度'],['ip_rating','IP'],['finish','表面'],['mounting','安装'],['dimming','调光'],['material','材质'],['remark','备注']];return '<div class="form-grid">'+f.map(x=>'<div class="field '+(x[0]==='intro'||x[0]==='remark'?'span3':'')+'"><label>'+x[1]+'</label>'+(x[0]==='intro'||x[0]==='remark'?'<textarea id="ov_'+x[0]+'">'+esc(ov[x[0]]||'')+'</textarea>':'<input id="ov_'+x[0]+'" value="'+esc(ov[x[0]]||'')+'">')+'</div>').join('')+'<div class="field span3"><button class="primary" onclick="saveOverride()">保存并刷新PDF预览</button></div></div>'}
async function saveOverride(){if(!state.current)return;let keys=['title','intro','product_family','model_display','dimensions','cutout','power','luminous_flux','efficacy','voltage','cct','cri','beam_angle','ip_rating','finish','mounting','dimming','material','remark'];let body={naming_model_id:state.current.id,model_no:state.current.model_no};keys.forEach(k=>body[k]=$('ov_'+k).value);try{state.current=await api('save_override',{method:'POST',headers:{'Content-Type':'application/json'},body:JSON.stringify(body)});renderDetail(state.current);refreshPdf();msg('已保存')}catch(e){msg(e.message,true)}}
function renderFiles(rows){let hi=(state.current.highres_images||[]);let html='<h3>高清图片（直接上传图片，通常 3 张）</h3><form id="hdUploadForm" class="form-grid" enctype="multipart/form-data"><input type="hidden" name="model_no" value="'+esc(state.current.model_no)+'"><input type="hidden" name="naming_model_id" value="'+esc(state.current.id)+'"><input type="hidden" name="file_type" value="高清图片"><input type="hidden" name="visibility" value="customer"><div class="field"><label>图片名称</label><input name="file_title" placeholder="HD Image"></div><div class="field span3"><label>上传高清图片</label><input type="file" name="files[]" multiple accept="image/*,.zip"></div><div class="field span3"><label>说明</label><input name="note" placeholder="产品细节图 / 场景图 / 客户资料图"></div><div class="field span3"><button type="button" class="primary" onclick="uploadNamedForm(\'hdUploadForm\',\'高清图片已上传\')">上传高清图片</button></div></form>';html+='<div class="image-grid">';if(!hi.length)html+='<div class="empty">暂无高清图片。</div>';hi.forEach(f=>{html+='<div class="image-tile"><img src="'+esc(f.url)+'" onclick="openImagePreview(\''+esc(f.url)+'\',\'高清图片\')"><b>'+esc(f.file_title||f.original_name||'HD Image')+'</b><small>'+esc(f.uploaded_at||'')+'</small></div>'});html+='</div><h3>其它资料文件</h3><form id="uploadForm" class="form-grid" enctype="multipart/form-data"><input type="hidden" name="model_no" value="'+esc(state.current.model_no)+'"><input type="hidden" name="naming_model_id" value="'+esc(state.current.id)+'"><div class="field"><label>资料类型</label><select name="file_type"><option>IES</option><option>LDT</option><option>测试报告</option><option>证书</option><option>安装说明</option><option>CAD/DWG</option><option>其它</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>权限</label><select name="visibility"><option value="customer">可发客户</option><option value="internal">内部资料</option><option value="customer_specific">指定客户</option><option value="forbidden">禁止外发</option></select></div><div class="field"><label>资料名称</label><input name="file_title"></div><div class="field span3"><label>选择文件</label><input type="file" name="files[]" multiple></div><div class="field span3"><label>说明</label><input name="note"></div><div class="field span3"><button type="button" class="primary" onclick="uploadFiles()">上传资料</button></div></form><h3>已上传资料</h3><div class="file-list">';let other=(rows||[]).filter(f=>!String(f.file_type||'').match(/高清|图片|配件|附件|配光|曲线/i));if(!other.length)html+='<div class="empty">暂无其它资料</div>';other.forEach(f=>{html+='<div class="item"><b>'+esc(f.file_type)+' · '+esc(f.file_title||f.original_name)+'</b><small>'+esc(f.original_name)+'<br>权限：'+esc(f.visibility)+' ｜ 上传：'+esc(f.uploaded_by)+' '+esc(f.uploaded_at)+'</small><div class="item-actions"><a class="btn" target="_blank" href="datasheet_api.php?action=download_file&id='+encodeURIComponent(f.id)+'">打开/下载</a>'+(state.perms.delete_file?'<button class="danger" onclick="deleteFile('+f.id+')">删除</button>':'')+'</div></div>'});html+='</div>';$('tab-files').innerHTML=html}
function renderAccessories(p){let webAcc=p.website_accessories||[];let manual=p.manual_accessories||[];let html='<p class="source-note">配件图来自公共配件图库。先在顶部上传到配件图库；这里搜索、预览并确认配对到当前型号。一个配件图可复用多个型号。</p>'; if(webAcc.length){html+='<h3>官网同步配件</h3><div class="acc-list">'+webAcc.map(a=>'<div class="item"><b>'+esc((a.model_no?a.model_no+' · ':'')+(a.name_en||a.name_cn||'Accessory'))+'</b><small>官网同步 ｜ 自动进入 PDF ACCESSORIES 区</small>'+(a.image_url?'<img class="mini-thumb2" src="'+esc(a.image_url)+'">':'')+'</div>').join('')+'</div>';} html+='<h3>当前型号配件图</h3><p class="tiny-note">不要在这里新建库；需要新增公共配件图请点顶部“上传配件图库”。</p><form id="accUploadForm" style="display:none" class="form-grid" enctype="multipart/form-data"><input type="hidden" name="model_no" value="'+esc(state.current.model_no)+'"><input type="hidden" name="naming_model_id" value="'+esc(state.current.id)+'"><input type="hidden" name="file_type" value="配件图片"><input type="hidden" name="visibility" value="customer"><div class="field"><label>配件名称</label><input name="file_title" placeholder="蜂巢网 / 四叶片 / Anti-glare Cover"></div><div class="field span3"><label>上传配件图片</label><input type="file" name="files[]" multiple accept="image/*,.zip"></div><div class="field span3"><label>型号/说明</label><input name="note" placeholder="可写配件型号或英文说明"></div><div class="field span3"><button type="button" class="primary" onclick="uploadNamedForm(\'accUploadForm\',\'配件图已上传\')">上传配件图并刷新PDF</button></div></form><div class="image-grid">'; if(!manual.length)html+='<div class="empty">当前产品暂无手动配件图。</div>'; manual.forEach(a=>{html+='<div class="image-tile"><img src="'+esc(a.image_url)+'" onclick="openImagePreview(\''+esc(a.image_url)+'\',\'配件图\')"><b>'+esc(a.name_en||a.name_cn||a.file_title||'Accessory')+'</b><small>'+esc(a.model_no||a.original_name||'')+'</small></div>'}); html+='</div><h3>从公共配件图库搜索并确认配对</h3><div class="form-grid"><div class="field span3"><label>模糊查找</label><input id="accFileKw" placeholder="型号 / 蜂巢网 / 四叶片 / honeycomb / shutter" onkeydown="if(event.key===\'Enter\')searchAccessoryImages()"></div><div class="field"><label>&nbsp;</label><button type="button" onclick="searchAccessoryImages()">搜索配件图</button></div></div><div id="accFileResults" class="acc-list"><div class="empty">输入关键词搜索公共配件图库，找到后确认配对到当前产品。</div></div>'; $('tab-acc').innerHTML=html}
function renderCurves(p){
let rows=p.photometric_images||[], webRows=p.website_photometric_images||[];
let html='<p class="source-note">配光曲线 PDF 只显示图片格式 JPG / PNG / WEBP / GIF，IES/LDT 属于光度数据文件，请在“资料”选项卡下载管理，不会作为图片显示进 PDF。</p>';
